graph LR
    Feast[Feast Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Feast -->|container orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]
    Feast -->|runtime| Python[Python 3.11]
    Feast -->|operator runtime| Go[Go 1.22]
    Feast -->|persistent storage| Storage[Storage Backend<br/>SQLite/Postgres/Snowflake<br/>S3/GCS/Cassandra]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Feast -.->|external routing| OpenShiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes 4.x]
    Feast -.->|TLS cert mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    Feast -->|custom CA certs| ODHTrustedCA[ODH Trusted CA Bundle]
    Feast -.->|mTLS & traffic mgmt| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio]
    Feast -.->|user authentication| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth]

    %% Integration Points - ODH Components
    ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| Feast
    DataSciencePipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|automated deployment| Feast
    JupyterNotebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -->|training features| Feast
    ModelServing[Model Serving<br/>KServe] -->|inference features| Feast

    %% External Services
    Feast -->|model storage| S3Service[S3 Storage]
    Feast -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Feast -.->|user auth| OIDCProvider[OIDC Provider<br/>Keycloak/OpenShift]
    Feast -.->|feature definitions| GitRepo[Git Repository<br/>GitHub/GitLab]
    Feast -.->|metrics| PrometheusService[Prometheus]

    %% Storage Backends (detailed)
    Storage -->|online store| Redis[Redis/Cassandra<br/>DynamoDB/SQLite]
    Storage -->|offline store| CloudStorage[S3/GCS/Snowflake<br/>BigQuery]
    Storage -->|registry store| RegistryBackend[S3/DB/File System]

    %% Styling
    style Feast fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
